        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Now them that are such we command and exhort by",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (or, as the best manuscripts read, ",
        "children": []
