        "text": "; in him, as the source of authority; \"In his Name.\" ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "That with quietness.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " In contrast to being busybodies, with calmness of spirit, freedom from excitement. ",
        "children": []
